column2: "Thank goodness, you two are okay! Really, I'm glad..."
"For the data I collected to be used like that... really, I'm sorry."
"...She's okay. She's been trying her hardest all this time, so she's just tired."
"Leave Matoi to me. <%me>, you must still have something to do."
"5章 たったひとつのやりかた"
